<html lang='en'>

  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Account Activation - Golden Bubbles</title>

    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f7f9fb;
        font-family: 'Poppins', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        color: #2b2b2b;
      }

      .email-container {
        max-width: 680px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }

      .header {
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 50px 0 0 0;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 28px;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        background: linear-gradient(
          to bottom,
          #c8a951 0%,
          #f9f6df00 30%,
          #ffffff00 100%
        );
      }

      .header img {
        width: 140px;
        height: auto;
        max-width: 100%;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 40px 50px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      .content h2 {
        color: #c19b3b;
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-top: 30px;
        border-left: 4px solid #c19b3b;
        padding-left: 10px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .credentials {
        background: transparent;
        border: 1px solid #f3e3b2;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 15px 20px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .credentials p {
        margin: 5px 0;
        color: #2b2b2b;
      }

      ul {
        margin: 15px 0 15px 20px;
        padding-left: 18px;
      }

      ul li {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      a {
        color: #c19b3b;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #f3f3f3;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #666;
        letter-spacing: 0.3px;
      }

      /* --- Mobile Fixes --- */
      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .email-container {
          margin: 20px 10px;
          border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .header {
          font-size: 20px;
          padding: 30px 15px 10px 15px;
        }

        .header img {
          width: 100px; /* ✅ smaller logo on mobile */
        }

        .content {
          padding: 25px 20px;
          font-size: 14px;
        }

        ul {
          margin: 10px 0 10px 15px; /* ✅ reduce left space for bullet list */
          padding-left: 15px;
        }
      }
    </style>

  </head>

  <body>
    <div class='email-container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <img
          src='https://d3s0ge8micz9n0.cloudfront.net/prod1/image/72/1761294164005-c35af3d9-895a-42b9-b1a7-96cf3557c31b.png'
          alt='Golden Bubbles Logo'
          width='140'
        />
        <!-- <div>Golden Bubbles</div> -->
      </div>

      <div class='content'>
        <p><strong>Dear {{firstName}},</strong></p>
        <p>We are delighted to confirm that your trading account with
          <strong>Golden Bubbles</strong>
          has been successfully activated.</p>

        <h2>Account Access</h2>
        <p>You may now log in securely with your credentials to view and manage
          your trading activities.</p>

        <div class='credentials'>
          <p><strong>Username:</strong> {{username}}</p>
          <p><strong>Password:</strong> {{password}}</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Key Information to Note</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Stop-Out Policy:</strong>
            If your margin level reaches the stop-out threshold, the system will
            automatically close open positions starting from the largest losing
            trades.</li>
          <li><strong>Weekend Margin Requirement:</strong>
            Ensure your margin level remains above 100% at Friday’s market close
            to prevent automatic closures.</li>
          <li><strong>Leverage & Incentives:</strong>
            Leverage levels and bonuses are subject to adjustment or withdrawal
            without prior notice, in accordance with our Terms and Conditions.</li>
          <li><strong>Security Reminder:</strong>
            Keep your login credentials private. Golden Bubbles will never ask
            for your password or offer personal trading advice.</li>
          <li><strong>Hedged Accounts:</strong>
            Accounts with partial hedging are treated the same as standard
            accounts and remain subject to stop-out rules.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Client Acknowledgment</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>You are solely responsible for monitoring and managing your
            trading positions.</li>
          <li>Golden Bubbles is not responsible for margin calls or account
            losses.</li>
          <li>You understand the risks of trading leveraged products, including
            the possibility of losing more than your initial deposit.</li>
          <li>You have reviewed and accepted our Terms and Conditions, Privacy
            Policy, and Risk Disclosure.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>For assistance, feel free to reach us at
          <a
            href='mailto:info@thegoldenbubbles.com'
          >info@thegoldenbubbles.com</a>.</p>

        <p style='margin-top:30px;'>Best regards,<br /><strong>Golden Bubbles
            LLC</strong></p>
      </div>
      <div class='footer'>
        &copy; 2025 Golden Bubbles LLC. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>

</html>